{% extends 'base.html.twig' %}

{% set title = "Committee" %}

{% block body %}
<div class="container pad-top">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-12">
            <h2 class="thin">MUTTS Committee 2024/25</h2>
            <p class="lead">The Committee are responsible for the day-to-day running of MUTTS, with each elected officer given particular responsibilities. They can be contacted individually via their email addresses below, or alternatively you can email the entire committee at <a href="mailto:committee@mutts.org.uk">committee@mutts.org.uk</a>.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row mb-5">
        <div class="col-md-1"></div>
        <div class="col-md-5 bio">
            <img class="rounded-circle" src="img/committee/rachel.jpg" alt="Chair" width="200" height="200">
            <h2>Rachel Crane</h2>
            <h3>Chair</h3>
            <p class="lead"><a href="mailto:chair@mutts.org.uk">chair@mutts.org.uk</a></p>
            <p>Rachel is a second year Drama and English Literature student. Her goal as chair is to make MUTTS a safe space for everyone to learn about technical theatre, no experience required. As Chair she is responsible for chairing committee meetings, taking overall responsibility for the society and its activities and working with other committee members on tasks such as organising training and ensuring the adequate staffing of events.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-5 bio">
            <img class="rounded-circle" src="img/committee/reuben.jpg" alt="Hire Manager" width="200" height="200">
            <h2>Reuben Vasey-Saunders</h2>
            <h3>Hire Manager</h3>
            <p class="lead"><a href="mailto:hire@mutts.org.uk">hire@mutts.org.uk</a></p>
            <p><b>DESCRIPTION</b> As hire manager, it is his job to oversee all hires, making sure the project managers feel supported in their role. He also manages MUTTS' equipment, making sure that we can meet the highest standards.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row mb-5">
        <div class="col-md-1"></div>
        <div class="col-md-5 bio">
            <img class="rounded-circle" src="img/committee/sam_fixed.jpg" alt="Treasurer" width="200" height="200">
            <h2>Sam Jackson</h2>
            <h3>Treasurer</h3>
            <p class="lead"><a href="mailto:treasurer@mutts.org.uk">treasurer@mutts.org.uk</a></p>
            <p>Sam is a third year Politics and Economics student, and it is his fourth year in MUTTS. As treasurer he'll be responsible for the societyâ€™s finances.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-5 bio">
            <img class="rounded-circle" src="img/committee/will_fixed.jpg" alt="Secretary" width="200" height="200">
            <h2>Matt Sale</h2>
            <h3>Secretary</h3>
            <p class="lead"><a href="mailto:secretary@mutts.org.uk">secretary@mutts.org.uk</a></p>
            <p><b>DESCRIPTION</b> As Secretary, he will be overseeing day to day organisation of the society.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row mb-5">
        <div class="col-md-1"></div>
        <div class="col-md-5 bio">
            <img class="rounded-circle" src="img/committee/luca.jpg" alt="social sec" width="200" height="200">
            <h2>Luca Wright</h2>
            <h3>Social Secretary &amp; Inclusion Officer</h3>
            <p class="lead"><a href="mailto:social@mutts.org.uk">social@mutts.org.uk</a></p>
            <p>Luca is a third year Computer Science and Maths student. As Social Secretary and Inclusion officer it is their role to organise events within the society and ensure that everyone feels welcome and happy at MUTTS. This year they hope that they can increase the number of dedicated social events and bring in plenty of new members.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-5 bio">
            <img class="rounded-circle" src="img/committee/arjun_fixed.jpg" alt="Crew Liason" width="200" height="200">
            <h2>Arjun Patel</h2>
            <h3>Crew Liason</h3>
            <p class="lead"><a href="mailto:crew@mutts.org.uk">crew@mutts.org.uk</a></p>
            <p>Arjun is a third year economics student who joined MUTTS last year. As the Crew Liason he is responsible for maintaining the crew and show operator rota for hires</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
{% endblock %}
